{"image_id": "WDC_2016_page_52", "image_size": [1238, 1613], "ocr": [{"text": "48", "bbox": [608.7, 1484.9, 629.5, 1505.8]}, {"text": "In the course of finalizing this Annual Report on Form 10-K, we determined it was necessary to record an", "bbox": [187.6, 147.9, 1093.3, 168.7]}, {"text": "additional $10 million in R&D expense primarily for third party non-recurring engineering charges and $5 million", "bbox": [150.1, 172.9, 1093.2, 193.7]}, {"text": "in asset impairment for the discontinuation of a software project for the fourth quarter and full year of fiscal 2016", "bbox": [150.1, 197.9, 1093.2, 218.7]}, {"text": "that were not included in our Current Report on Form 8-K filed with the SEC on July 28, 2016 to announce our", "bbox": [150.1, 222.9, 1093.0, 243.8]}, {"text": "preliminary and unaudited financial results for the fourth fiscal quarter and fiscal year ended July 1, 2016. Given this", "bbox": [150.1, 247.9, 1093.1, 268.8]}, {"text": "change, for fiscal year 2016, operating income decreased to $466 million and net income decreased to $242 million,", "bbox": [150.1, 272.9, 1093.1, 293.8]}, {"text": "or $1.00 per diluted share, and for the fourth quarter of 2016, operating loss increased to $195 million and net loss", "bbox": [150.1, 297.9, 1093.3, 318.8]}, {"text": "increased to $366 million, or $1.40 per diluted share.", "bbox": [150.1, 322.9, 579.0, 343.8]}, {"text": "The following is a summary of our financial performance for fiscal 2016:", "bbox": [187.6, 364.6, 765.4, 385.5]}, {"text": "• In 2016, our net revenue decreased by 11% to $13.0 billion on HDD shipments of 185 million units, as", "bbox": [187.6, 406.3, 1093.2, 427.1]}, {"text": "compared to $14.6 billion on shipments of 229 million units in 2015.", "bbox": [212.6, 431.3, 774.7, 452.2]}, {"text": "• HDD ASPs increased to $61 in 2016, as compared to $60 in 2015.", "bbox": [187.6, 473.0, 749.8, 493.8]}, {"text": "• Gross profit as a percentage of net revenue decreased to 26.4% in 2016, as compared to 29.0% in 2015.", "bbox": [187.6, 514.7, 1041.5, 535.5]}, {"text": "• Operating income decreased to $466 million in 2016, as compared to $1.6 billion in 2015. Operating income", "bbox": [187.6, 556.4, 1093.1, 577.2]}, {"text": "in 2016 included $345 million of employee termination, asset impairment and other charges, as compared to", "bbox": [212.6, 581.4, 1093.2, 602.2]}, {"text": "$176 million in 2015. In addition, operating income in 2016 included SanDisk acquisition-related costs of", "bbox": [212.6, 606.4, 1093.2, 627.2]}, {"text": "$159 million and charges related to cost savings initiatives of $143 million.", "bbox": [212.6, 631.4, 818.9, 652.2]}, {"text": "• Net income in 2016 was $242 million, or $1.00 per diluted share, as compared to $1.5 billion, or $6.18 per", "bbox": [187.6, 673.1, 1093.1, 693.9]}, {"text": "diluted share, in 2015.", "bbox": [212.6, 698.1, 395.0, 718.9]}, {"text": "Summary Comparison of 2016, 2015 and 2014", "bbox": [168.8, 739.7, 523.6, 760.5]}, {"text": "The following table sets forth, for the periods presented, selected summary information from our consolidated", "bbox": [187.6, 781.4, 1093.1, 802.3]}, {"text": "statements of income by dollars and percentage of net revenue:", "bbox": [150.1, 806.4, 650.2, 827.3]}, {"text": "Years Ended", "bbox": [728.9, 851.7, 815.5, 868.4]}, {"text": "July 1, 2016", "bbox": [519.6, 875.2, 601.6, 891.8]}, {"text": "July 3, 2015", "bbox": [732.2, 875.2, 814.2, 891.8]}, {"text": "June 27, 2014", "bbox": [937.3, 875.2, 1032.3, 891.8]}, {"text": "(in millions, except percentages)", "bbox": [692.8, 900.1, 872.5, 916.7]}, {"text": "Net revenue. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [150.1, 922.9, 452.3, 943.7]}, {"text": "$ 12,994", "bbox": [477.3, 922.9, 550.2, 943.7]}, {"text": "100.0%", "bbox": [597.1, 922.9, 661.4, 943.7]}, {"text": "$ 14,572", "bbox": [689.9, 922.9, 762.8, 943.7]}, {"text": "100.0%", "bbox": [809.7, 922.9, 874.0, 943.7]}, {"text": "$ 15,130", "bbox": [902.4, 922.9, 9